&lt;html&gt;
	&lt;head&gt;
		&lt;title&gt;&lt;/title&gt;
	&lt;/head&gt;
	&lt;body&gt;
		&lt;div title=&quot;align-text: center; max-width: 100%; margin-left: 0; margin-right: 0&quot;&gt;
			&lt;h2 style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;
				&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:22px&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Smartphone SAMSUNG Galaxy A12 Mem&amp;oacute;ria Interna 64GB Azul C&amp;acirc;mera Quadrupla 48MP 4GB de Ram Tela 6.5&amp;quot; SM-A127&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
			&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;
				&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
			&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;
				&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;Tela Infinita de 6.5&amp;quot;**&lt;br /&gt;
				C&amp;acirc;mera Qu&amp;aacute;drupla Traseira de 48MP + 5MP + 2MP + 2MP&lt;br /&gt;
				Selfie de 8MP&lt;br /&gt;
				64GB de Mem&amp;oacute;ria Interna(*) e 4GB RAM&lt;br /&gt;
				Bateria de 5.000mAh&lt;br /&gt;
				Dual Chip, Dual Messenger&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
			&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;
				&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
			&lt;h3 style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;
				&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Mais display significa mais espa&amp;ccedil;o para jogar&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
				&lt;br /&gt;
				Expanda sua vis&amp;atilde;o com o Infinity-V Display de 6,5 polegadas do Galaxy A12 e veja o que voc&amp;ecirc; estava perdendo. Gra&amp;ccedil;as &amp;agrave; tecnologia HD+, seu conte&amp;uacute;do di&amp;aacute;rio fica n&amp;iacute;tido e claro.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
			&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;
				&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;https://statics.angeloni.com.br/eletro/conteudo/samsung/galaxy-a127-1.jpg&quot; style=&quot;max-width: 1000px; width: 100%;&quot; /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
				&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10px&quot;&gt;*Imagem simulada para fins ilustrativos.&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10px&quot;&gt;**Medido na diagonal, o tamanho da tela &amp;eacute; de 6,5&amp;quot; como um ret&amp;acirc;ngulo inteiro e de 6,4&amp;quot; considerando os cantos arredondados. A &amp;aacute;rea vis&amp;iacute;vel real &amp;eacute; menor devido aos cantos arredondados e ao orif&amp;iacute;cio da c&amp;acirc;mera.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
			&lt;h3 style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;
				&lt;br /&gt;
				&lt;br /&gt;
				&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Design combinando estilo e conforto&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
			&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;
				&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;O Galaxy A12 combina est&amp;eacute;tica de design simplificada com cores cl&amp;aacute;ssicas. As curvas refinadas o tornam confort&amp;aacute;vel de segurar e proporcionam navega&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o f&amp;aacute;cil na tela. Escolha entre as cores preta, branca, vermelha e azul.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
			&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;
				&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;https://statics.angeloni.com.br/eletro/conteudo/samsung/galaxy-a127-2.jpg&quot; style=&quot;max-width: 1000px; width: 100%;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
			&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;
				&lt;p&gt;
					&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
				&lt;div&gt;
					&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Melhore sua fotografia m&amp;oacute;vel com a c&amp;acirc;mera qu&amp;aacute;drupla&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
				&lt;div&gt;
					&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
				&lt;div&gt;
					&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;Capture momentos memor&amp;aacute;veis com detalhes n&amp;iacute;tidos com a c&amp;acirc;mera principal de 48 MP. Expanda o &amp;acirc;ngulo de vis&amp;atilde;o com a c&amp;acirc;mera Ultra Wide. Personalize o foco com a c&amp;acirc;mera de profundidade ou fique mais perto dos detalhes com a c&amp;acirc;mera macro.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
				&lt;p&gt;
					&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;https://statics.angeloni.com.br/eletro/conteudo/samsung/galaxy-a127-3.jpg&quot; style=&quot;max-width: 400px; width: 100%;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
				&lt;div&gt;
					&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10px;&quot;&gt;*A disponibilidade da cor pode variar conforme o pa&amp;iacute;s ou a operadora.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
				&lt;div&gt;
					&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
			&lt;/div&gt;
			&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;
				&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
			&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;
				&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
			&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;
				&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;C&amp;acirc;mera Ultra Wide para grandes momentos&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
			&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;
				&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
			&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;
				&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;Semelhante &amp;agrave; vis&amp;atilde;o humana, a c&amp;acirc;mera Ultra Wide de 5 MP v&amp;ecirc; o mundo com um &amp;acirc;ngulo de vis&amp;atilde;o de 123 graus, adicionando mais perspectiva a tudo o que voc&amp;ecirc; fotografa.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
			&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;
				&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;https://statics.angeloni.com.br/eletro/conteudo/samsung/galaxy-a127-4.jpg&quot; style=&quot;max-width: 1000px; width: 100%;&quot; /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
				&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10px&quot;&gt;*Imagem simulada para fins ilustrativos. **A utiliza&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o do modo ultra wide (fotos/v&amp;iacute;deos) &amp;eacute; suportada apenas pela c&amp;acirc;mera traseira.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
			&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;
				&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
			&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;
				&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
			&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;
				&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
			&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;
				&lt;h3&gt;
					&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;A c&amp;acirc;mera macro foca nos pequenos detalhes&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
				&lt;div&gt;
					&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;Chegue mais perto com a c&amp;acirc;mera macro de 2 MP e descubra os pequenos detalhes que voc&amp;ecirc; teria perdido. Ela aplica o efeito Bokeh natural &amp;agrave;s suas fotos, permitindo que o objeto se destaque do fundo.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
				&lt;div&gt;
					&lt;br /&gt;
					&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;https://statics.angeloni.com.br/eletro/conteudo/samsung/galaxy-a127-5.jpg&quot; style=&quot;font-size: 16px; max-width: 400px; width: 100%;&quot; /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
					&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10px;&quot;&gt;*Imagem simulada para fins ilustrativos. **O recurso da c&amp;acirc;mera macro &amp;eacute; suportado apenas pela c&amp;acirc;mera traseira.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
			&lt;/div&gt;
			&lt;h3 style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;
				&amp;nbsp;&lt;/h3&gt;
			&lt;h3 style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;
				&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Coloque o foco na frente com a c&amp;acirc;mera de profundidade&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
			&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;
				&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;A c&amp;acirc;mera de profundidade de 2 MP permite ajustar a profundidade de campo das suas fotos. Com um simples toque, voc&amp;ecirc; pode ajustar facilmente o desfoque de fundo atr&amp;aacute;s do objeto para tirar retratos de alta qualidade que realmente se destacam.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
			&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;
				&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;https://statics.angeloni.com.br/eletro/conteudo/samsung/galaxy-a127-6.jpg&quot; style=&quot;max-width: 1000px; width: 100%;&quot; /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
				&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10px&quot;&gt;*Imagem simulada para fins ilustrativos.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
			&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;
				&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
			&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;
				&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
			&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;
				&lt;div&gt;
					&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
				&lt;div&gt;
					&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;C&amp;acirc;mera frontal, selfies que chamam a aten&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
				&lt;div&gt;
					&lt;br /&gt;
					&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;Com a c&amp;acirc;mera frontal de 8 MP e o Live Focus do Galaxy A12, &amp;eacute; f&amp;aacute;cil tirar selfies incr&amp;iacute;veis com mais voc&amp;ecirc; e menos fundo.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
				&lt;div&gt;
					&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
				&lt;p&gt;
					&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;https://statics.angeloni.com.br/eletro/conteudo/samsung/galaxy-a127-7.jpg&quot; style=&quot;max-width: 400px; width: 100%;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
				&lt;div&gt;
					&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10px;&quot;&gt;*Imagem simulada para fins ilustrativos.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
				&lt;div&gt;
					&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
			&lt;/div&gt;
			&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;
				&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
			&lt;h3 style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;
				&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;Bateria duradoura&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
			&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;
				&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;Fique &amp;agrave; frente do dia com uma bateria que n&amp;atilde;o atrasar&amp;aacute; voc&amp;ecirc;. A bateria de 5.000 mAh (padr&amp;atilde;o)* permite que voc&amp;ecirc; continue fazendo o que faz por horas a fio. Com at&amp;eacute; 15 W de carregamento r&amp;aacute;pido e adapt&amp;aacute;vel, o Galaxy A12 estar&amp;aacute; completamente recarregado com rapidez.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
			&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;
				&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
			&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;
				&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;https://statics.angeloni.com.br/eletro/conteudo/samsung/galaxy-a127-8.jpg&quot; style=&quot;max-width: 1000px; width: 100%;&quot; /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
				&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10px&quot;&gt;*Valor padr&amp;atilde;o testado em condi&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es de laborat&amp;oacute;rio terceirizado. O valor padr&amp;atilde;o &amp;eacute; o valor m&amp;eacute;dio estimado considerando o desvio na capacidade da bateria entre as amostras de bateria testadas sob o padr&amp;atilde;o IEC 61960. A capacidade nominal (m&amp;iacute;nima) &amp;eacute; de 4.900 mAh. A dura&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o real da bateria pode variar dependendo do ambiente de rede, padr&amp;otilde;es de uso e outros fatores. **Adaptador Adaptive Fast Charging fornecido na caixa.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
			&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;
				&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
			&lt;h3 style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;
				&lt;br /&gt;
				&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;Tenha mais espa&amp;ccedil;o para jogar&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
			&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;
				&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;O Galaxy A12 combina com o poder de processamento do octa-core com at&amp;eacute; 4GB de mem&amp;oacute;ria RAM para um desempenho r&amp;aacute;pido e eficiente para a tarefa. Aproveite 64GB de armazenamento interno.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
			&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;
				&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
			&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;
				&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;https://statics.angeloni.com.br/eletro/conteudo/samsung/galaxy-a127-9.jpg&quot; style=&quot;max-width: 1000px; width: 100%;&quot; /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
				&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10px&quot;&gt;*A mem&amp;oacute;ria RAM e a capacidade de armazenamento interno podem variar conforme o pa&amp;iacute;s. O armazenamento real dispon&amp;iacute;vel pode variar conforme os softwares pr&amp;eacute;-instalados.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
			&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;
				&lt;br /&gt;
				&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
			&lt;h3 style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;
				&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Concentre-se com o One UI Core&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
				&lt;br /&gt;
				O One UI Core ajuda voc&amp;ecirc; a focar no que &amp;eacute; realmente importante. Hardware e software trabalham juntos, com conte&amp;uacute;dos e recursos na ponta de seus dedos para voc&amp;ecirc; encontr&amp;aacute;-los mais rapidamente. Use o Modo Noturno para ter uma experi&amp;ecirc;ncia confort&amp;aacute;vel no escuro, e com visuais simples e intuitivos, usar seu celular &amp;eacute; natural.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
				&lt;br /&gt;
				&amp;nbsp;&lt;/h3&gt;
			&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;
				&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;https://statics.angeloni.com.br/eletro/conteudo/samsung/galaxy-a127-10.jpg&quot; style=&quot;max-width: 1000px; width: 100%;&quot; /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
				&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10px&quot;&gt;*A disponibilidade do recurso One UI Core, aplicativos e servi&amp;ccedil;os pode variar conforme o dispositivo, a vers&amp;atilde;o do sistema operacional e o pa&amp;iacute;s. **A imagem do dispositivo e da tela &amp;eacute; simulada para fins ilustrativos.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
			&lt;h3 style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;
				&lt;br /&gt;
				&lt;br /&gt;
				&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Seguran&amp;ccedil;a com n&amp;iacute;vel de defesa. Protege o que &amp;eacute; importante para voc&amp;ecirc;.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
				&lt;br /&gt;
				Incorporado ao hardware e ao software do celular desde o in&amp;iacute;cio, o Samsung Knox protege seu celular a partir do momento em que &amp;eacute; ligado. Oferecendo v&amp;aacute;rias camadas de seguran&amp;ccedil;a, ele defende suas informa&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es sens&amp;iacute;veis contra malware e amea&amp;ccedil;as maliciosas.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
			&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;
				&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;https://statics.angeloni.com.br/eletro/conteudo/samsung/galaxy-a127-11.jpg&quot; style=&quot;max-width: 1000px; width: 100%;&quot; /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
				&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10px&quot;&gt;*Arquitetura de medi&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o integrada (Integrity Measurement Architecture) baseada em TrustZone.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
			&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;
				&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
			&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;
				&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
			&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;
				&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
			&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;
				&lt;h3&gt;
					&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;Uma experi&amp;ecirc;ncia sempre incr&amp;iacute;vel com o Android&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
				&lt;div&gt;
					&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;Tenha os aplicativos Google mais recentes no sistema operacional Android, totalmente compat&amp;iacute;veis com seu Galaxy A12.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
			&lt;/div&gt;
			&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;
				&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;https://statics.angeloni.com.br/eletro/conteudo/samsung/galaxy-a127-12.jpg&quot; style=&quot;max-width: 500px; width: 100%;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
			&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;
				&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10px;&quot;&gt;*A disponibilidade dos aplicativos Google pode variar dependendo do pa&amp;iacute;s ou idioma.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
			&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;
				&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
			&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;
				&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
			&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;
				&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
			&lt;h3 style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;
				&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;Sempre a seu dispor, a qualquer momento e em qualquer lugar&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
			&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;
				&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
			&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;
				&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;Aproveite a tranquilidade ao comprar um smartphone Galaxy. Os diagn&amp;oacute;sticos interativos e a otimiza&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o do aplicativo Samsung Members facilitam a melhoria de desempenho dos seus dispositivos, enquanto nossa linha de assist&amp;ecirc;ncia permite a resolu&amp;ccedil;&amp;atilde;o de problemas quando voc&amp;ecirc; precisar de assist&amp;ecirc;ncia extra.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
			&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;
				&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
			&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;
				&lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;https://statics.angeloni.com.br/eletro/conteudo/samsung/galaxy-a127-13.jpg&quot; style=&quot;max-width: 1000px; width: 100%;&quot; /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
				&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:10px&quot;&gt;*As fun&amp;ccedil;&amp;otilde;es e os recursos dispon&amp;iacute;veis no aplicativo Samsung Members podem variar conforme o pa&amp;iacute;s e o dispositivo. **Dispositivo e imagens simulados para fins ilustrativos.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
			&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;
				&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
			&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;
				&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
			&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;
				&lt;span style=&quot;font-size:16px&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Dimens&amp;otilde;es do Aparelho (mm):&lt;/strong&gt; 164 x 75.8 x 8.9&lt;br /&gt;
				&lt;strong&gt;Peso do Aparelho (g): &lt;/strong&gt;205&lt;br /&gt;
				&lt;strong&gt;Dimens&amp;otilde;es da Caixa Unit&amp;aacute;ria (mm): &lt;/strong&gt;170 x 82 x 49.1&lt;br /&gt;
				&lt;strong&gt;Peso da Caixa Unit&amp;aacute;ria (g):&lt;/strong&gt; 400&lt;br /&gt;
				&lt;strong&gt;Dimens&amp;otilde;es da Caixa Master (mm): &lt;/strong&gt;334 x 243 x 185&lt;br /&gt;
				&lt;strong&gt;Formato do Aparelho: &lt;/strong&gt;Barra&lt;br /&gt;
				&lt;strong&gt;Interface com o Usu&amp;aacute;rio: &lt;/strong&gt;Touch Screen&lt;br /&gt;
